# Cerebron MCP Integration for Cursor

# Add this to your Cursor MCP settings (Settings → MCP Servers → Add):
#
# {
#   "name": "cerebron",
#   "url": "http://localhost:8080/mcp"
# }
#
# Available tools:
#   analyze_incident           — correlate signals for a service
#   find_similar_incidents     — search incident history by fingerprint or service
#   detect_incident_trends     — frequency and severity trends across services
#   get_service_dependencies   — upstream/downstream graph and blast radius
#   analyze_causal_hints       — deterministic causal heuristics (deployment triggers, DB latency)
#   get_recent_deployments     — deployments across all configured CI/CD providers
#   get_incident_history       — full incident history for a service
